    • getRawType

      JRawType getRawType()
      Returns the raw type for this generic type. The raw type removes all 'generics' information from the class. i.e. void a1(List<T>) invalid input: '&' void a2(List<String>) becomes void a1(List) invalid input: '&' void a2(List)) respectively.
